{"type":"message","id":"4c78e8a7","parentId":"55ba64ee","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:51:38.900Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有找到memory文件，说明没有上下文信息。用户没有指定具体的竞品名称，这是一个问题。\n\n作为竞品分析师，我应该：\n1. 明确竞品是谁\n2. 但作为subagent，我应该尽量自主完成任务\n\n由于任务描述是\"竞品上线了AI协同功能\"，这可能是：\n- 协同办公软件（如Notion、飞书、钉钉等）\n- 项目管理工具\n- 设计协作工具\n- 代码协作平台\n\n最可能的情况是协同办公软件，因为\"AI协同功能\"这个描述最符合这类产品。\n\n让我做一个快速的市场调研，搜索近期主流AI协同办公产品的更新和用户反馈。我会搜索：\n1. AI协同功能 最新上线 2026\n2. 主要竞品可能包括：Notion AI、飞书AI、钉钉AI、Microsoft Copilot等\n\n由于用户说\"竞品上线了AI协同功能\"，这可能指的是某个特定产品最近发布的新功能。让我搜索最近上线的AI协同功能相关的新闻。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有找到背景信息。您提到\"竞品上线了AI协同功能\"，但没有指定具体是哪个竞品。\n\n让我搜索近期AI协同办公领域的主要动态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-4f7f85a206424b99b19492887cbc9d69","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"AI协同功能 上线 2026 最新 竞品","count":5,"freshness":"pw"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e4bc0e6586c84f8abf9b3512602daeef","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Notion AI Copilot 飞书AI 钉钉AI 协作功能对比 2026","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":341,"output":529,"cacheRead":10934,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11804,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772779885998}}
{"type":"message","id":"1181fc5a","parentId":"4c78e8a7","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:51:38.913Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-4f7f85a206424b99b19492887cbc9d69","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_kimi_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (kimi) needs a Moonshot API key. Set KIMI_API_KEY or MOONSHOT_API_KEY in the Gateway environment, or configure tools.web.search.kimi.apiKey.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_kimi_api_key","message":"web_search (kimi) needs a Moonshot API key. Set KIMI_API_KEY or MOONSHOT_API_KEY in the Gateway environment, or configure tools.web.search.kimi.apiKey.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772779898910}}
