{"type":"message","id":"e541a023","parentId":"c2984257","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:52:23.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"DuckDuckGo搜索失败了（可能是网络问题或bot检测）。让我尝试使用其他方式：\n\n1. 使用multi-search-engine skill\n2. 或者直接使用web_fetch访问一些知名网站\n\n让我先看看multi-search-engine skill。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-1d13739eba894c3c8c23efb8853fee14","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":98,"output":126,"cacheRead":12771,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772779939730}}
{"type":"message","id":"c022d2e1","parentId":"e541a023","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:52:23.932Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-1d13739eba894c3c8c23efb8853fee14","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772779943914}}
{"type":"message","id":"101e3bcb","parentId":"c022d2e1","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:52:30.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我可以使用web_fetch直接访问搜索引擎。让我尝试几个搜索：\n1. 百度搜索（国内搜索效果可能更好）\n2. Google搜索（国际搜索）\n\n由于任务比较紧急，我会同时发起多个搜索请求，然后汇总结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-d67ce4f93223433287fbdf9f3ef06f1b","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=AI协同办公功能+最新上线+2026","maxChars":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-0aa2e2a2a1aa4282be9d3196b5c786d4","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.google.com/search?q=AI+collaboration+workspace+features+2026+recent+launch","maxChars":15000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-a6b80fed004446dcacd79323d0340ec7","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=飞书AI+钉钉AI+企业微信AI+协同功能+用户评价","maxChars":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"alibaba","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1060,"output":224,"cacheRead":12868,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14152,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772779943933}}
